'''''SeaDream I''''' is a yacht-style  [[cruise ship]] operated by [[SeaDream Yacht Club]] since 2001.<ref name="ta 2014-05-03"/>  

In service since 1984, she was formerly named ''Sea Goddess I'' and operated for Sea Goddess Line and Cunard. In January 2000 she was transferred to Seabourn <ref>https://www.chriscunard.com/history-fleet/cunard-fleet/1960-today/sea-goddess-i/</ref>, becoming''Seabourn Goddess I''.  She is a sister ship to ''[[SeaDream II]]''.<ref name="ta 2014-05-03"/>

